{
  "stem": "7094.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Because when you talk, first of all, you have to have a sympathetic listener to be able to talk.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Secondly, you don't want to talk about yourself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I don't want any sympathy from anybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I was tough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Life toughened me, and it happened so that I survived, not because I was clever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Not because I was-- it's just a coincidence played a part.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "You know, there wasn't a design in it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "It was just one step after another.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "But I want to talk about the people who did not survive, people who were wiped out, who-- I don't even have a photograph of my sisters.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "This is something that-- that I want people to be aware what-- the danger that can happen, because it is there all the time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "My survival-- these experiences and my liberation were very dramatic, and also left an indelible mark.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Because it happened when I was liberated, because it all happened, so I took it as a-- as a-- as-- to justify my guilt of survival.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "Because it's there all the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "I feel guilty that I live.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And very often, when I'm very depressed and things are going very badly, I think, it's good for me to-- to-- to-- to bear the pain.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "Because I think the few moments I could have been with my mother were more worthwhile than all my existence after that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "But I had to learn how to live with it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And I thought I've done quite-- [LAUGHS] I'm sorry I'm not very good at your interview.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I thought that I'll be able to tell you this story bravely, because I couldn't have done this before.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "But I thought I'd-- but yet it touches this inner nerve.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "So I apologize for that.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
